CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F422A1774959066
OL,3,CMan arrested on suspicion of murder of
OL,4,C17-year-old girl last seen in 1998
OL,6,FDetectives investigating her
OL,7,Fdisappearance and suspected murder
OL,8,Fhave been carrying out inquiries in
OL,9,Fthe city in recent weeks.
OL,11,FDonna was last seen in Middlesbrough
OL,12,Fon April 28 1998 and was known to have
OL,13,Ftravelled to Leeds that year.
OL,15,FSenior investigating officer Detective
OL,16,FChief Inspector Steven Chatterton
OL,17,Fsaid: "This morning we have made an
OL,18,Farrest as a result of our recent
OL,19,Finquiries, and the man remains in
OL,20,Fpolice custody at this time for
OL,21,Fquestioning.
OL,26,@yD@GOU
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G2/5
