PN,42203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F422A1774959066
OL,3,CMan arrested on suspicion of murder of
OL,4,C17-year-old girl last seen in 1998
OL,6,F"I would like to reiterate our appeal
OL,7,Ffor anyone to contact us who may have
OL,8,Fseen Donna, spoken to her, or knows
OL,9,Fanything about her movements in Leeds
OL,10,Fin 1998 to come forward.
OL,12,F"We are in close contact with Donna's
OL,13,Ffamily and they have lived with
OL,14,Funbearable uncertainty for nearly 30
OL,15,Fyears.
OL,17,F"We are determined to find out what
OL,18,Fhappened to Donna for them.
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@AOUyD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G3/5
